c: 12
v: 42
t: "Sano jwalakwe (Yusufu) ŵansalile ajula jwaŵammanyi kuti chajokoche mwa ŵaŵilio (yanti): “Nkakumbuchile kungolanga kwa abwana ŵenu (Afiriauna kuti angoposye mu ukaidi muno).” Basi shetani ŵan’diŵesye jwalakwejo kolanga (ya Yusufu) kwa abwana ŵakwe. Basi ni ŵatemi (Yusufu) mu ukaidi yaka igala"